# ── Week 5 additions to .env.local ──────────────────────────────────────────

# Resend (email) — get from https://resend.com/api-keys
RESEND_API_KEY=re_YOUR_KEY_HERE
RESEND_FROM_EMAIL=noreply@yourdomain.com
# ^ Must be a verified domain in Resend, or use their test domain:
#   onboarding@resend.dev (100 emails/day, no domain verification needed)


# ── Setup checklist ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# 1. Run migrations in order via Supabase SQL Editor:
#    - 003_notifications.sql   (notifications + preferences tables)
#    - 004_enable_realtime.sql (enables live postgres_changes subscriptions)

# 2. Sign up for Resend (free): https://resend.com
#    - For instant testing: use RESEND_FROM_EMAIL=onboarding@resend.dev
#    - For production: verify your own domain (takes ~10 min via DNS)

# 3. Apply INTEGRATION_PATCH.tsx changes:
#    - Swap static status badges for <RealtimeSubmissionStatus />
#    - Confirm triggerAIValidation() fires in createSubmission()

# 4. Replace these files from earlier weeks with their Week 5 versions:
#    - app/actions/triage.ts                (now sends notifications)
#    - app/api/ai/validate-submission/route.ts (now notifies org on completion)
#    - components/layout/header.tsx          (now has live NotificationBell)

# 5. Test the full loop:
#    a. Open two browser windows (or one normal + one incognito)
#    b. Window A: log in as researcher, submit a report
#    c. Window B: log in as org owner — watch notification bell update LIVE
#    d. Window B: open the submission, click Accept
#    e. Window A: watch the status badge flip to "Accepted" with a toast
#    f. Check both inboxes for the corresponding emails


# ── Cost check ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
